trans-unit.source: Provides a <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"></xref> object used at design time to apply control skins to controls.
trans-unit.target: Gir et <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"> </xref> objekt under utformingen for kontrollen skallene gjelder kontroller.

trans-unit.source: Page developers and control authors do not use the SkinBuilder class directly.
trans-unit.target: Siden utviklere og kontroll forfattere bruker ikke klassen SkinBuilder direkte.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET designer builders use the SkinBuilder class in conjunction with the <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider> class and the <xref:System.Web.UI.IThemeResolutionService> interface to apply themes and their respective control skins to controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET designer verktøy Bruk klassen SkinBuilder sammen med den <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider>klassen og <xref:System.Web.UI.IThemeResolutionService>grensesnittet skal gjelde tema og de respektive kontrollen skallene Kontroller under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.IThemeResolutionService> </xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider>

trans-unit.source: To apply themes at design time, the base <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.ApplyTheme%2A> method whenever a control's child control tree is built.
trans-unit.target: Bruke oppsett under utformingen grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasse kall den <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.ApplyTheme%2A>metoden når en kontroll underordnede kontrollen tre bygges.</xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.ApplyTheme%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder"></xref> class, setting the control with which the builder is associated, the general <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"></xref> object provided by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider"></xref> object for the control, and a path to the theme file.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder"> </xref> klasse, angi kontrollen som er tilknyttet, Generelt <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider"> </xref> objekt for kontrollen, og en bane til temafil.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is called by the <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider.GetSkinBuilder%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider> class to return a <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder> object for the control specified in the `control` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren kalles av den <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider.GetSkinBuilder%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider>klassen for å returnere en <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder>objekt for kontrollen som er angitt i den `control` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider> </xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider.GetSkinBuilder%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider"></xref> that encapsulates theme information for controls in a designer environment.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider"> </xref> som innkapsler temainformasjon for kontroller i et miljø med designer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> with which the <xref href="System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder"></xref> is associated.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> som den <xref href="System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder"> </xref> er knyttet til.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.ApplyTheme*> method applies a control skin to this control and returns it.
trans-unit.target: Til <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.ApplyTheme*>metoden bruker en kontroll verktøylinje til denne kontrollen, og returnerer det.</xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.ApplyTheme*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"></xref> provided by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider"></xref> for the control's type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"> </xref> fra den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider"> </xref> for kontrollens typen.

trans-unit.source: The absolute path to the theme file.
trans-unit.target: Den absolutte banen til filen tema.

trans-unit.source: Applies a theme and a control skin to the current control at design time, if a <xref href="System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder"></xref> object is associated with the control.
trans-unit.target: Gjelder et tema og en kontroll verktøylinje for gjeldende kontroll på utformingstidspunktet, hvis en <xref href="System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder"> </xref> objektet som er knyttet til kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder> objects are associated with controls at design time by specifying an <xref:System.Web.UI.IThemeResolutionService> instance for the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> object of a control that supplies a <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider> object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder>objekter som er knyttet til kontroller under utformingen ved å angi en <xref:System.Web.UI.IThemeResolutionService>serverforekomsten den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>objekt til en kontroll som gir en <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.IThemeResolutionService></xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider> object can return a <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder> object for a given control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider>objekt kan returnere en <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder>objekt for en gitt kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeProvider>

trans-unit.source: The control instance to which the theme or style sheet theme and any control skin was applied.
trans-unit.target: Kontroll-forekomsten som oppsettet eller stilen arket tema og alle kontrollere verktøylinje ble brukt.

trans-unit.source: This is the same instance passed to the builder's <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Dette er den samme forekomsten ble sendt til builder <xref:System.Web.UI.SkinBuilder.%23ctor%2A> konstruktør.

trans-unit.source: This method will return <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if no control was passed to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden tilbakestiller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis ingen kontroll ble sendt til konstruktøren.
